Description
----------------------------

The Board Game Collector is an online library of boardgames, it's purpose it to allow users to make an account and save individual baordgames
to their collection. They can then easily show which games they own to other gamers with the clear way BGC presents boardgames!

Models & Their Properties
----------------------------

1. User Model
    + name
    + email
    + password

2. Boardgame Model
    + title
    + image
    + year
    + rating

3. Boardgame-Instance -> (This will eventually let you log when you play a game, so you and other users can see which
    + boardgame           games you play the most!)
    + play

